### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@studentEmail = estudiante@universidad.edu
@habitId = 1

### 1) Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2) Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 3) API root
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
Accept: application/json

###

### 4) Listar habitos (GET collection)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/students/{{studentEmail}}/habitos
Accept: application/json

###

### 5) Obtener un habito por ID (GET resource)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/students/{{studentEmail}}/habitos/{{habitId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 6) Crear habito (POST collection -> 201 + Location)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/students/{{studentEmail}}/habitos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Dormir mejor",
  "meta": "8 horas diarias",
  "icon": "😴",
  "motivo": "Recuperacion fisica",
  "dias": ["L", "M", "X", "J", "V"]
}

###

### 7) Actualizar parcialmente (PATCH resource)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/students/{{studentEmail}}/habitos/{{habitId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meta": "7.5 horas diarias",
  "motivo": "Mejor energia en clases"
}

###

### 8) Reemplazo completo (PUT resource)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/students/{{studentEmail}}/habitos/{{habitId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Lectura profunda",
  "meta": "45 min / dia",
  "icon": "📘",
  "motivo": "Aprender mas rapido",
  "dias": ["L", "M", "X", "J", "V", "S"]
}

###

### 9) Eliminar habito (DELETE resource -> 204)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/students/{{studentEmail}}/habitos/{{habitId}}